==古生物学==
===颅骨装饰===
[[File:Cryolophosaurus_Frozen_Crest_Restoration.jpg|alt=]]
对有社会行为的群居动物如冰冠龙来说，颅骨展示特征是存在意义的，物种成员可据此观察并领会其它个体的性状态信息。<ref name="Dodson_Paleoeco">{{cite book|last=Dodson|first=P.|year=1997|chapter=Paleoecology|editor1-last=Currie|editor1-first=P.J.|editor2-last=Padian|editor2-first=K.|title=Encyclopedia of Dinosaurs|publisher=Academic Press|isbn=978-0-12-226810-6}}</ref>{{le|凯文·帕迪安|Kevin Padian}}（Kevin Padian）等人（2004年）挑战传统假说，即恐龙奇怪的颅骨结构及颅后装甲的作用要么是吸引配偶，要么是威胁兽群中的竞争对手，或者是恐吓其它物种的潜在捕食者，提出根据系统发育、组织学和功能证据，这些奇异结构的功能可通过{{le|种内识别|Intra-species recognition}}现象来解释，该现象亦得到化石证据的支持。<ref name=glut2006>{{cite book|last=Glut|first=D.F.|year=2006|title=Dinosaurs, the Encyclopedia, Supplement 4|publisher=McFarland & Company, Inc|page=749|isbn=978-0-7864-2295-1}}</ref><ref name=padian>{{cite journal|last1=Padian|first1=K.|last2=Horner|first2=J.R.|last3=Dhaliwal|first3=J.|year=2004|title=Species recognition as the principal cause of bizarre structures in dinosaurs|journal=Journal of Vertebrate Paleontology|volume=23|issue=3 Suppl |page=100A|doi=10.1080/02724634.2003.10010538|s2cid=220410105}}</ref>[[托马斯·霍兹（Thomas R. Holtz Jr.）（2010年）发现，根据近缘物种证据和骨骼纹理研究，冰冠龙的奇异头冠主要用于种内识别。<ref name="Holtz2012">{{cite book|last=Holtz|first=T.R. Jr.|year=2012|title=Dinosaurs: The Most Complete, Up-to-Date Encyclopedia for Dinosaur Lovers of All Ages|publisher=Random House Books for Young Readers|url=https://archive.org/details/dinosaursmostcom00holt/page/90|pages=[https://archive.org/details/dinosaursmostcom00holt/page/90 90–91]|isbn=978-0-375-82419-7|url-access=registration}}</ref>托马斯·里奇（Thomas Rich）和同事的研究认为头冠无法当作武器使用，但可能在某些类型的社会行为（如交配）中起展示作用。<ref name="rich-gang-ham_1997">{{cite book|last1=Rich|first1=T.R.|last2=Gangloff|first2=R.A.|last3=Hammer|first3=W.R.|year=1997|chapter=Polar dinosaurs|editor1-last=Currie|editor1-first=P.J.|editor2-last=Padian|editor2-first=K.|title=Encyclopedia of Dinosaurs|publisher=Academic Press|pages=562–573|isbn=978-0-12-226810-6}}</ref>该假说在2019年受到争议，又但提出了社会性展示结构模型。<ref name="Yun2019">{{cite journal |last=Chan-gyu |first=Yun. |year=2019 |title=An enigmatic theropod ''Cryolophosaurus'': Reviews and Comments on its paleobiology |journal=Volumina Jurassica |volume=17 |pages=1–8}}</ref>

===饮食===
正模标本刚发现时，在其口中发现几根疑似原蜥脚类恐龙的细长颈肋，哈默（1998年）由此得出结论称冰冠龙死前正在吃一只原蜥脚类，并进一步指出，由于发现肋骨一直伸进标本颈部区域，因此这只冰冠龙可能是被肋骨噎死。<ref name="hammer1998"/>然而，史密斯等人指出这些肋骨属于冰冠龙自身而非哈默声称的“原蜥脚类”。<ref name="smithetal2007"/>哈默还认为标本中发现的一颗[[三瘤齿兽科|三瘤齿兽科]]（早期哺乳类近亲）犬齿生前是其胃容物的一部分。<ref name=glut1999>{{cite book|last=Glut|first=D.F.|year=1999|title=Dinosaurs, the Encyclopedia, Supplement 1|publisher=McFarland & Company, Inc|page=442|isbn=978-0-7864-0591-6}}</ref>

===古病理学===
[[File:Juvenile_Cryolophosaurus_Teeth.jpg|thumb]]
一些冰冠龙骨骼的病理显示出被食腐动物清理的迹象。附近发现一只幼龙的断牙。<ref name="rich-gang-ham_1997" />这些牙齿没有根部，很可能是在进食成年冰冠龙尸体时自然脱落。

[[File:Cryolophosaurus_Left_Tibia_Fossil.jpg|thumb]]

另一疑似病理发现于冰冠龙的距骨上，该骨骼与踝骨上方[[腓骨|腓骨]]的一个小夹层一起保存。然而，夹层也可能只是该属的一个独特形态特征。<ref name="Smithetal2007b" />

==古生态学==
[[File:CryolophosaurusDB.jpg|upright]]
所有已知冰冠龙标本皆发现于汉森组，它是南极大陆发现的仅有的两个主要含恐龙地层之一。化石在大约1.94至1.88亿年前<ref name="smithetal2013"/><ref name=evans>{{cite book|last1=Evans|first1=D.C.|last2=Vavrek|first2=M.J.|year=2012|title=Ultimate Dinosaurs: Giants from Gondwana|publisher=Toronto:Royal Ontario Museum|pages=30–1}}</ref>早侏罗世锡内穆阶至普连斯巴奇阶时期沉积的凝灰质粉砂岩中发现。<ref name="hammer1998"/>该[[地层|地层]]是高出海平面{{convert|4000|m}}的横贯南极山脉维多利亚群（Victoria Group）的一部分。<ref name="hammer1998"/>该地区海拔较高，支持早侏罗世南极洲的[[森林|森林]]中至少沿海岸居住着多种多样的物种的观点。<ref name="dodson_97b"/><ref name=holtz2004>{{cite book|last1=Holtz|first1=T.R. Jr.|last2=Molnar|first2=R.E.|last3=Currie|first3=P.J.|year=2004|chapter=Basal Tetanurae|editor1-last=Weishampel|editor1-first=D.B.|editor2-last=Dodson|editor2-first=P.|editor3-last=Osmólska|editor3-first=H.|title=The Dinosauria (Second ed.)|publisher=University of California Press|isbn=978-0-520-24209-8|pages=71–110}}</ref>汉森组沉积在[[冈瓦纳古陆|冈瓦纳古陆]]解体期间形成的活火山构造分裂系统中。<ref name="smithetal2007">{{Cite journal| last=Smith | first=N. D.| author2=Makovicky, P.J.| author3= Pol, D.| author4= Hammer, W.R.| author5= Currie, P.J.| year=2007| journal = US Geological Survey Open-File Report| title = The Dinosaurs of the Early Jurassic Hanson Formation of the Central Transantarctic Mountains: Phylogenetic Review and Synthesis| volume=2007| issue=1047srp003| doi = 10.3133/of2007-1047.srp003 }}</ref>

在早侏罗世，南极洲离[[赤道|赤道]]更近而且世界比今天温暖得多，但[[气候|气候]]仍非常[[气温|凉爽]]。<ref name=pickrell2004>{{cite news|last=Pickrell|first=John|title=Two New Dinosaurs Discovered in Antarctica|url=http://news.nationalgeographic.com/news/2004/03/0309_040309_polardinos.html|access-date=20 December 2013|newspaper=National Geographic|year=2004}}</ref>侏罗纪气流模型表明当时南极沿海地区气温可能从未降到冰点以下太多，尽管内陆存在更极端的条件。<ref name="chandler">{{Cite journal | last1 = Chandler | first1 = M. A. | last2 = Rind | first2 = D. | last3 = Ruedy | first3 = R. | doi = 10.1130/0016-7606(1992)104<0543:PCDTEJ>2.3.CO;2 | title = Pangaean climate during the Early Jurassic: GCM simulations and the sedimentary record of paleoclimate | journal = Geological Society of America Bulletin | volume = 104 | issue = 5 | pages = 543 | year = 1992 | bibcode = 1992GSAB..104..543C }}</ref>冰冠龙是在距[[南极点|南极点]]约{{convert|650|km|mi}}处发现，但其生前的栖息地还要靠北约{{convert|1000|km|abbr=on}}。<ref name="dodson_97b">{{cite book|last=Dodson|first=P.|year=1997|chapter=Distribution and Diversity|editor1-last=Currie|editor1-first=P.J.|editor2-last=Padian|editor2-first=K.|title=Encyclopedia of Dinosaurs|publisher=Academic Press|pages=10–13|isbn=978-0-12-226810-6}}</ref>该地层已出土[[冰河龙|冰河龙]]<ref name=SP07>{{cite journal |last=Smith |first=Nathan D. |author2=Pol, Diego |year=2007 |title=Anatomy of a basal sauropodomorph dinosaur from the Early Jurassic Hanson Formation of Antarctica |journal=Acta Palaeontologica Polonica |volume=52 |issue=4 |pages=657–674 |url=http://app.pan.pl/acta52/app52-657.pdf }}{{dead link|date=December 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>（一种大型基干[[蜥脚形亚目|蜥脚形亚目]]）、一种乌鸦大小的[[翼龙|翼龙]]（一种[[双型齿翼龙科|双型齿翼龙科]]）、[[合弓纲|合弓纲]]（一种[[三瘤齿兽科|三瘤齿兽科]]，为老鼠大小的合弓纲）、一种植食性合弓纲和两种未命名的小型蜥脚形亚目。<ref name="hammer&hickerson1994"/>还有许多从早侏罗世{{le|坎普山组|Camp Hill Formation}}发现的植物遗骸，化石年龄与冰河龙大致相同，证明南极洲向南漂移之前，其表面曾生长过茂盛的植物。<ref name=rees2004>{{cite journal|authors=Rees, P.M. & Cleal, C.J.|title=Lower Jurassic floras from Hope Bay and Botany Bay, Antarctica|journal=Special Papers in Palaeontology|year=2004|volume=72|pages=5–90|url=http://www.geo.arizona.edu/~rees/reesclealhbproofs.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100722083349/http://www.geo.arizona.edu/~rees/reesclealhbproofs.pdf|url-status=dead|archive-date=2010-07-22}}</ref>

